{"data":[{"name":"91:1","price":"Juro por el Sol cuando resplandece,","arabic":"وَٱلشَّمۡسِ وَضُحَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6044,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:2","price":"por la Luna cuando lo refleja,","arabic":"وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا تَلَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6045,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:3","price":"por el día cuando fulgura,","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا جَلَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6046,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:4","price":"por la noche cuando cubre con su oscuridad,","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا يَغۡشَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6047,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:5","price":"por el cosmos y la creación maravillosa que hay en él,","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَمَا بَنَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6048,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:6","price":"por la Tierra y su vasta extensión,","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَمَا طَحَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6049,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:7","price":"por el alma y su armonía,","arabic":"وَنَفۡسٖ وَمَا سَوَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6050,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:8","price":"[Dios] le enseñó [al ser humano] a distinguir entre el pecado y la conciencia de Dios.","arabic":"فَأَلۡهَمَهَا فُجُورَهَا وَتَقۡوَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6051,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:9","price":"¡Será bienaventurado quien purifique su alma [apartándola de los pecados],","arabic":"قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن زَكَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6052,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:10","price":"pero será un desventurado quien la abandone a sus pasiones!","arabic":"وَقَدۡ خَابَ مَن دَسَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6053,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:11","price":"El pueblo de Zamud rechazó el Mensaje por soberbia.","arabic":"كَذَّبَتۡ ثَمُودُ بِطَغۡوَىٰهَآ","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6054,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:12","price":"Cuando el más opresor de ellos se prestó para matar a la camella.","arabic":"إِذِ ٱنۢبَعَثَ أَشۡقَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6055,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:13","price":"El Mensajero de Dios [Sálih] los previno: \"No maten a la camella de Dios [enviada como milagro] y déjenla abrevar libremente\".","arabic":"فَقَالَ لَهُمۡ رَسُولُ ٱللَّهِ نَاقَةَ ٱللَّهِ وَسُقۡيَٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6056,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:14","price":"Pero desmintieron al Mensajero y mataron a la camella. Entonces, su Señor los destruyó a todos, por lo que cometieron, con un castigo arrasador,","arabic":"فَكَذَّبُوهُ فَعَقَرُوهَا فَدَمۡدَمَ عَلَيۡهِمۡ رَبُّهُم بِذَنۢبِهِمۡ فَسَوَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6057,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"91:15","price":"sin temor por la magnitud de Su castigo.","arabic":"وَلَا يَخَافُ عُقۡبَٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6058,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"}],"chapter":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams","Chapter Ash-Shams","Shams","Surah Shams","Chapter Shams","Ash Shams","Surah Ash Shams","Chapter Ash Shams","Surah 91","Chapter 91","The Sun","الشمس"]}